---
const steps = [
	{
		title: '1. Choose the matter type',
		copy: 'Start with the service lane first so the form can narrow the right questions immediately.',
	},
	{
		title: '2. Answer the fit questions',
		copy: 'Share only the core facts, timing, and contact details the firm needs for a real first review.',
	},
	{
		title: '3. Get the next step',
		copy: 'If it fits, the next move is usually an email with scheduling instructions and the $100 30-minute consultation link.',
	},
];
---

<div class="panel intake-panel">
	<p class="mini-kicker">3-Step Intake Path</p>
	<h2 class="mini-title">How requests usually move.</h2>
	<p class="mini-copy">Most people finish the intake in about 2 to 4 minutes.</p>
	<ol class="intake-steps">
		{
			steps.map((step) => (
				<li>
					<strong>{step.title}</strong>
					<span>{step.copy}</span>
				</li>
			))
		}
	</ol>
	<p class="mini-copy">Most requests are reviewed within 1 business day when submitted on a business day.</p>
</div>
